### Component Details

#### [NEW] [config.py](file:///Users/ayushman/Documents/CODES/IE4228_Grp5/Assignment2/src/facerec/config.py)

Central configuration dataclass:
- Model names and weight paths (with auto-download fallback)
- Detection confidence threshold (default 0.5)
- Recognition similarity threshold (default 0.35)
- Image size for alignment (112×112)
- Device selection (CPU for Mac prototyping, CUDA for NSCC)

