#### [NEW] [detector.py](file:///Users/ayushman/Documents/CODES/IE4228_Grp5/Assignment2/src/facerec/detector.py)

Two detector backends via `insightface`:
- **RetinaFace** (ResNet-50 backbone) — high accuracy
- **SCRFD** (10GF variant) — high speed

Interface:
```python
class FaceDetector:
    def __init__(self, model_name: str = "retinaface_r50_v1", device: str = "cpu")
    def detect(self, image: np.ndarray) -> list[Detection]
    # Detection = dataclass(bbox, confidence, landmarks_5pt)
```

This satisfies rubric 1 "Compares ≥2 detectors" for **Excellent**.

