#### [NEW] [recognizer.py](file:///Users/ayushman/Documents/CODES/IE4228_Grp5/Assignment2/src/facerec/recognizer.py)

Embedding extraction using `insightface` model zoo:
```python
class FaceRecognizer:
    def __init__(self, model_name: str = "arcface_r100", device: str = "cpu")
    def get_embedding(self, aligned_face: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray  # 512-d
    def compute_similarity(self, emb1, emb2) -> float  # cosine sim
```

Supports ArcFace (R100) by default; AdaFace via custom weight loading for NSCC fine-tuning.

